pqiv
------------------------------------------
A very simple PyGTK image viewer, meant as a replacement for qiv. Its 
features are limited to fullscreen, slideshows, rotate, scale and 
mirror.

Runtime requirements:
  python-2.5.1-1
  python-gobject2-2.12.3-2
  python-gtk2-2.10.4-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.pberndt.com/Programme/Linux/pqiv/index.html

Canonical download:
  http://www.pberndt.com/Programme/Linux/pqiv/_download/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack pqiv-0.2-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./pqiv-0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pqiv-0.2-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/pqiv-0.2-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/bin/pqiv
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/pqiv-0.2.README
  /usr/share/doc/pqiv-0.2/GPL.txt
  /usr/share/doc/pqiv-0.2/README
  /usr/share/man/man1/pqiv.1.gz

